      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "We have micro-benchmarks available (checked into Gson subversion repository under trunk/metrics directory) that show that on simple object conversions, the low-level streaming API could be upto 10x faster. There are other benchmarks too (which I need to encourage the original author to publish) that this low-level API currently beats other libraries including Jackson. However, creating comprehensive and representative benchmarks is going to take some time and effort."
