  "title" : "Jackson Vs. Gson",
  "body" : "<p>After searching through some existing libraries for JSON, I have finally ended up with these two:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Jackson</li>\n<li>Google GSon</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>I am a bit partial towards GSON, but word on the net is that GSon suffers from a certain celestial performance <a href=\"http://www.cowtowncoder.com/blog/archives/2009/09/entry_326.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">issue</a> (as of Sept 2009).</p>\n\n<p>I am continuing my comparison; in the meantime, I'm looking for help to make up my mind.</p>\n"
